desc.BF_001: Prevents enemies from focusing on a single ally. Action order increases after defending. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_002: A combo-oriented formation. BP cost -1 after a combo. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_003: A combo-oriented formation. BP cost -3 after defeating a foe. BP increases by 1 after combos.
desc.BF_004: Avoid those combos! Increases all allies' attack. BP cost -3 after defeating a foe. BP increases by 3 each turn. Resets after combos.
desc.BF_005: A defensive formation. BP cost -1 after defending. Sacrifices all allies' attack for defense. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_006: Excels at both offense and defense. 1st position targeted more; 5th targeted less. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_007: Ally in 1st position acts as a decoy. 1st position defense up; 2nd–5th down. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_008: Acts swiftly in ascending position order. Tech BP cost -1 in the 1st position. BP increases by 1 each turn. Resistant to paralysis.
desc.BF_009: A formation where allies act slowly but in sequence. Action order increases upon defending. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_010: Tech BP cost -1 in 1st position. Resistant to darkness. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_011: Tech BP cost -1 in 1st position. Resistant to stun. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_012: Tech BP cost -1 in 5th position. Resistant to poison. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_013: Tech BP cost -1 in 5th position. Resistant to stench. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_014: Used by squires to protect spellcasters. 1st position conditional BP -1. 2nd position spell BP -1 and increased attack. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_015: Facilitates the casting of powerful spells. Spell BP cost -2 increased attack and increased defense in 5th position. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_016: Effective against flying foes.  Gathers allies to either end of the timeline. BP increases by 1 after combos.
desc.BF_017: Yield initiative in favor of conditionals and combos. Sacrifices all allies' attack for defense. BP increases by 1 after combos.
desc.BF_018: Allows for easy 2x combos. BP cost -1 after performing combos. BP increases by 1 after combos.
desc.BF_019: 1st position acts swiftly. Resistant to petrification. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_020: Firms up defenses at the end of the line. Increased defense in the 5th position. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_021: Ally in 3rd position draws enemy attacks. Attack down and defense up in 3rd position. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_022: Facilitates spellcasting and effective against airborne foes. Spell BP cost -1 increased attack and increased defense in 4th and 5th positions. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_023: Puts 1st position in the spotlight. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_024: 2nd 3rd and 4th positions have increased attack. All allies have decreased defense. BP increases by 1 after defeating foes by means other than poison or enemy actions.
desc.BF_025: Overwhelming spiritual power grants high starting BP but decreases all allies' attack and defense. BP does not change.
desc.BF_026: 1st and 2nd positions focus on finishing off foes. BP cost -1 in 3rd position. BP increases by 2 after defeating foes by means other than poison or enemy actions.
desc.BF_027: Facilitates the use of counterattacks and interrupts. 1st and 2nd positions are more easily targeted. BP increases by 1 after using counterattacks or interrupts.
desc.BF_028: Allies act slowly and sacrifice attack for defense. BP cost -1 in the 1st and 2nd positions. BP increases by 1 each turn.
desc.BF_029: Easy to disrupt enemy combos in 1st and 2nd positions. Resistant to confusion. BP increases by 1 each turn.
